  "heading_path": "光的干涉",
  "intensity": "STRUCTURAL",
  "line_count": 64,
  "masked_text": "[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02101:709a26eb5332]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02102:b4b736e86edb]]\n\n光的本性经历过一条很长的认识路线。\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02103:558149d9777b]]{波动性证据链}大致是这样的：\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02104:ff2eb9e78880]]{itemize}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02105:ab452bea72eb]] 牛顿曾提出微粒说，认为光是由光源发出的微粒流；\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02106:ab452bea72eb]] 惠更斯提出波动说，认为光是一种波；\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02107:ab452bea72eb]] 杨氏双缝实验直接观察到稳定干涉条纹，强有力地支持了光的波动性；\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02108:ab452bea72eb]] 麦克斯韦进一步指出，光本质上是一定频率范围内的电磁波。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02109:06b3847e1b6f]]{itemize}\n光是电磁波，其中电场 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02110:1eec4a6b8e82]] 和磁场 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02111:98c300e4b2ec]] 垂直于传播方向且互相垂直。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02112:ff2eb9e78880]]{itemize}\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02113:ab452bea72eb]] 光波中有一个振荡的电场 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02114:1eec4a6b8e82]]，它的振动方向就是光的[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02115:5e0ac999eea1]]\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02116:ab452bea72eb]]  光的强度（即能量流密度）正比于电场振幅的平方：[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02117:7f4683dec770]]；\n [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02118:ab452bea72eb]] 探测器接收到的是时间平均值 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02119:5cc0e9db265e]]，因为光的振荡频率远高于任何探测器的响应速度。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02120:06b3847e1b6f]]{itemize}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02121:2915695a4992]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02122:ff2eb9e78880]]{note}\n 题目只要说[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02123:649c2290dbb2]][[PROTECTED:F00001-P02124:6a82f5fac866]]，默认指的都是电场 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02125:1eec4a6b8e82]] 的方向； 它把后面偏振题里真正会被筛选、会被比较夹角的那个方向固定下来； 传播方向、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02126:1eec4a6b8e82]]、[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02127:98c300e4b2ec]] 两两垂直，而偏振片筛的是 [[PROTECTED:F00001-P02128:1eec4a6b8e82]] 在某个横向方向上的分量； 把[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02129:40df2a0cb518]]和[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02130:05c12777ab13]]混成同一个方向。\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02131:06b3847e1b6f]]{note}\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02132:e5ac5a6a87ec]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02133:1e4db1447dcd]]\n\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02134:ff2eb9e78880]]{center}\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02135:172af5d6ab88]]\n[[PROTECTED:F00001-P02136:06b3847e1b6f]]{center}\n",
